    <!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

  <meta charset="UTF-8" />

  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>My Website</title>

  <style>

    body {

      margin: 0;

      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;

      background: #0f172a;

      color: white;

      text-align: center;

    }

    header {

      padding: 60px 20px;

      background: #1e293b;

    }

    h1 {

      margin: 0;

      font-size: 40px;

    }

    p {

      font-size: 18px;

      color: #cbd5e1;

    }

    .btn {

      display: inline-block;

      margin-top: 20px;

      padding: 12px 20px;

      background: #38bdf8;

      color: black;

      text-decoration: none;

      border-radius: 8px;

      font-weight: bold;

    }

    section {

      padding: 40px 20px;

    }

    footer {

      padding: 20px;

      font-size: 14px;

      color: #94a3b8;

    }

  </style>

</head>

<body>

  <header>

    <h1>Welcome to My Website</h1>

    <p>This is my GitHub Pages site 🚀</p>

    <a class="btn" href="#about">Learn More</a>

  </header>

  <section id="about">

    <h2>About Me</h2>

    <p>

      i like to take walks play video games but i am also now learning how to lose weight 

    </p>

  </section>

  <section>

    <h2>My Projects</h2>

    <p>Add your GitHub projects here later.</p>

  </section>

  <footer>

    © 2026 My Website

  </footer>

</body>

</html>